{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.finished","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><em><code>finished</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>事件</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p>Animation.finished 只读属性允许您返回动画的完成状态。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> The Promise is replaced with a new (pending) Promise object every time the animation leaves the <code>finished</code> play state.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> animationsPromise <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>finished<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个 Promise 对象。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下代码会等到所有动画都完成，然后再移除它们处于活动状态的元素：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Promise<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAnimations</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>finished\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">remove</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-finished","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation.finished"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器支持","id":"浏览器支持","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.finished","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关内容","title":"相关内容","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">KeyframeEffect Interface (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器支持","id":"浏览器支持"},{"text":"相关内容","id":"相关内容"}],"summary":"Animation.finished 只读属性允许您返回动画的完成状态。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.finished","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},